Unit testing:
Test suites - collection of test cases

Libraries and frameworks for testing -
JavaScript - Jasmine, Mocha, Chai, Sinon, qUnit
React - jest
Test runner(executer) - Karma
enzyme - testing utility that mounts components by not actually mounting on the browser

Jasmine:
describe - a suite, is a function
it - a spec(test case), is also a function
toBe, toEqual, toMatch - matchers


1.install jasmine-core, karma, karma-jasmine
2.install karma-cli -g (karma.exe)